{"tid":921200,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"【第二波劈價】翔龍灣三百呎單位 兩個月唔見兩球","createTime":"2018-11-29T11:07:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-30T03:59:04.000Z","uid":174649,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"699dde3dbc2863937998e55b00e8baf12f8cbaa2","tid":921200,"uid":174649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T11:07:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20181129/large/1543484117_6051.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20181129%2Flarge%2F1543484117_6051.jpg&h=59fe76ec&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n消息指，土瓜灣翔龍灣6座低層B室，實用面積385方呎，兩房間隔，望內園景，原叫價660萬元，之後減至630萬元仍無人承接，一劈再劈，減至600萬元超低價終易手，呎價15,584元，創屋苑今年新低價。<br />\n<br />\n早幾個月買家最進取時期，翔龍灣兩房單位造價全逾700萬元，甚至要800萬元。如5座低層G室，實用面積385方呎，同樣內園景，今年9月以830萬元成交，呎價21,558元。相隔兩個月後，同面積單位造價大幅回落230萬元或28%。"},{"pid":"be3b98346f906ea6848da0293b41ad7ce9eae55d","tid":921200,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T11:33:59.000Z","msg":"樓下多團友 而家近大陸/接觸多大陸人既樓先值錢"},{"pid":"efe446dba84fb1c1f13a801aeb89027e5f0d164b","tid":921200,"uid":6297,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"be3b98346f906ea6848da0293b41ad7ce9eae55d","tid":921200,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T11:33:59.000Z","msg":"樓下多團友 而家近大陸/接觸多大陸人既樓先值錢"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T12:15:03.000Z","msg":"樓下做緊大型道路工程，唔計"},{"pid":"73c33bfe2eab64f64b197850e759654802cd0e66","tid":921200,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T13:19:23.000Z","msg":"又兩球 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bad2b366d094642769d4d66b14f2eb008649e3ca","tid":921200,"uid":159798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-29T13:30:56.000Z","msg":"如果年頭750萬賣左會唔會俾人笑落錯車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d65910ab49930725cc2d3bdbabe72415645610f","tid":921200,"uid":429